OL,3,CFare evasion costs Transport for
OL,4,CLondon #130m a year
OL,6,FAround one in 29 public transport
OL,7,Fusers in London do not pay the correct
OL,8,Ffare, figures show.
OL,10,FTransport for London (TfL) said 3.5%
OL,11,Fof passengers across its network evade
OL,12,Ffares, costing it #130 million
OL,13,Fannually.
OL,15,FThe figure has fallen from 3.8% in the
OL,16,F2023/24 financial year.
OL,18,FIn April, TfL announced new measures
OL,19,Faimed at slashing the figure to 1.5%
OL,20,Fby the end of the decade.
