OL,6,FThese include targeting the most
OL,7,Fprolific fare evaders and using
OL,8,Fadvanced technology.
OL,10,FShadow justice secretary Robert
OL,11,FJenrick posted a video on social media
OL,12,Fon Thursday in which he confronted
OL,13,Fpeople who forced their way through
OL,14,Fthe ticket barriers at Stratford
OL,15,Fstation in east London.
OL,17,FHe asked one person "do you think it's
OL,18,Fall right not to pay" and challenged
OL,19,Fanother to "go back through the
OL,20,Fbarrier and pay".
