OL,6,FSpeaking to BBC Radio 5 Live on
OL,7,FThursday, Mr Jenrick said staff
OL,8,F"weren't doing anything" to tackle
OL,9,Fevasion when he was at Stratford to
OL,10,Ffilm the video.
OL,12,F"They weren't either trained or didn't
OL,13,Fhave the self-confidence to take
OL,14,Faction, and I think that's the issue
OL,15,Fsometimes," he said.
OL,17,FLondon Underground and Overground
OL,18,Fservices operate from Stratford, as
OL,19,Fwell as mainline rail services, the
OL,20,FElizabeth line and the DLR.
