OL,6,FInterventions with fare dodgers are
OL,7,Finvolved in around half of reported
OL,8,Fincidents of violence and aggression
OL,9,Ftowards frontline staff, according to
OL,10,FTfL.
OL,12,FTrade union the Transport Salaried
OL,13,FStaffs' Association (TSSA) appeared to
OL,14,Faccuse Mr Jenrick of "trying to score
OL,15,Fpoints" with the clip.
OL,17,FIt said in a statement: "This incident
OL,18,Fwas not only inappropriate but also
OL,19,Fpotentially dangerous for passengers,
OL,20,Fstaff and the individual involved.
