OL,6,F"Fare evasion is a serious issue, but
OL,7,Fit must be tackled with professional,
OL,8,Ftrained enforcement, not MPs trying to
OL,9,Fscore points or social media clout on
OL,10,Ftheir daily commute."
OL,12,FSiwan Hayward, TfL's director of
OL,13,Fsecurity, policing and enforcement,
OL,14,Fsaid the "overwhelming majority" of
OL,15,Fpassengers pay the correct fare, but
OL,16,Fthere is "a minority who do attempt to
OL,17,Ftravel without a valid ticket, which
OL,18,Fis a criminal offence".
