OL,6,FShe went on: "Fare evasion is
OL,7,Funacceptable. That is why we are
OL,8,Fstrengthening our capability to deter
OL,9,Fand detect fare evaders, including
OL,10,Fexpanding our team of professional
OL,11,Finvestigators to target the most
OL,12,Fprolific fare evaders across the
OL,13,Fnetwork.
OL,15,F"This builds on the work of our team
OL,16,Fof more than 500 uniformed officers
OL,17,Falready deployed across the network to
OL,18,Fdeal with fare evasion and other anti-
OL,19,Fsocial behaviour, keeping staff and
OL,20,Fcustomers safe.
